Flint Energy Services, Sino-Forest: Canadian Equity Preview

-- B y   M a t t   W a l c o f f
-- 
2011-06-21T04:00:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/flint-energy-services-sino-forest-canadian-equity-preview.html
Shares of the following companies
may have unusual moves in Canadian trading.  Flint Energy Services Ltd. (FES)  : The oilfield-services
company had its rating raised to “market perform” from
“underperform” by Kevin Lo, an analyst at FirstEnergy Capital
Corp.  Sino-Forest Corp. (TRE)  : The forestry company fighting a
short seller’s assertions of financial manipulation may move
after Paulson & Co., formerly its largest shareholder, reported
selling all of its shares in the company.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nick Baker at 
 nbaker7@bloomberg.net  